<h2 id="&#x793A;&#x4F8B;">&#x793A;&#x4F8B;</h2>

<h3 id="&#x4F7F;&#x7528;_valueOf">&#x4F7F;&#x7528;&#xA0;<code>valueOf</code></h3>

<pre>function myNumberType(n) {
    this.number = n;
}

myNumberType.prototype.valueOf = function() {
    return this.number;
};

myObj = new myNumberType(4);
myObj + 3; // 7</pre>
